text: Nipponaphera suduirauti is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Cancellariidae, the nutmeg snails. ==References== * Bouchet P. & Petit R.E. (2008). New species and new records of southwest Pacific Cancellariidae. The Nautilus 122(1): 1-18. Category:Cancellariidae Category:Nipponaphera Category:Gastropods described in 1999
title: Nipponaphera suduirauti
